I feel like I never post anything, I need to be better at it this year.
I’m sorry if I’m adding more things to your feed ☺️.

Just realized there were too many images that I like on this editorial and I never posted them.

This was a story we did in LA with the coolest ⭐️ @sukiwaterhouse and @katetabakova ,who I love her vision and styling taste and we always know what each other likes. Miss you Kate!
We went to this dirty motel, had a cool car and the best crew, what else do we need…that’s usually 80% of a guaranteed great shoot.
Hair @robsalty
Make Up @kathyjeung 
Production @julia_orlova_production @alexeyg

Some films from when we shot this job in Marrakesh 🇲🇦 

I remember we decided at the last part of the shoot to get out of the hotel we were shooting and put @kim_vanderlaan interacting at the Medina. No surprise she looks so pretty and with her huge smile made every single person next to her feel happy and relaxed. I also remember the day before the job when were scouting we saw these kids playing some cards in the street, so we asked them if they could be at the same place at the same time the next day… they were so excited to be at this that we couldn’t stop shooting different variations of the same shot. 
Last thing I also remember was how hot it was, around 45c and the cameras and computer wouldn’t even work due to the heat. 
It was so worth it everyone’s effort, I still love this commercial job because of all the experiences and challenges, but most of all the image of happiness in everyone’s face. ❤️
